{"tid":1818111,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國際特赦組織要人！過關出事手足唔係condom！","createTime":"2020-01-09T15:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T09:23:38.000Z","uid":193592,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c431f4125478458d517694f4a71462c6b0be2bb5","tid":1818111,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJuWt77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJuWt77.jpg&h=93f43915&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HvYoTzP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvYoTzP.png&h=a2786884&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上幾個星期已有港人去澳門經洗頭橋被送中<br />\n而早排Simon Cheng番出黎都講<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">大陸公安已經認左捉左我地既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以其實送中係一直冇停過</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前幾個月我地推冧得監控燈柱<br />\n今舖有咩理由唔理過關有手足比人攞相兇呢單野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家中共可能係有個大數據系統<br />\n收集晒所有相再用人面識別記錄晒你一舉一動</span><br />\n你一過關就玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">早排成個連登都係講過大陸關點點點出事<br />\n宜家國際特赦組織想搵d過關曾經比人截停<br />\n加俾公安攞相話佢參與過係香港示威既人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">手足唔係condom阿，做野啦各位！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有 話晒國際特赦組織呢大半年都出左咁多聲（612同新屋嶺都有出報告 未睇自己google）<br />\n成日話要去海牙法庭指控警暴<br />\n又話要打國際陣線<br />\n而家有人權組織咁落力幫手發聲<br />\n唔該ching幫手推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你本人試過<br />\n又或者識得任何人有咁既經歷<br />\n幫個手出個聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算唔識 都幫手推同forward<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實只係用你幾秒<br />\n記住 咩都唔做係唔會自己贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b62f92998a8b9a111bf97bbf41460b0da8581ac","tid":1818111,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c431f4125478458d517694f4a71462c6b0be2bb5","tid":1818111,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJuWt77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJuWt77.jpg&h=93f43915&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HvYoTzP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvYoTzP.png&h=a2786884&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上幾個星期已有港人去澳門經洗頭橋被送中<br />\n而早排Simon Cheng番出黎都講<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">大陸公安已經認左捉左我地既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以其實送中係一直冇停過</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\